message.body: I'm potentially seeing into the woods tonight with my sister, but I'll let you know definitely around 2ish if that's okay.

Hey! I can go out tonight! We're actually going to the movies tomorrow! But if everyone can only go out tomorrow, then please do!!! Mike is going to be here all next week and then the 5th - 7th. Unfortunately, we won't be able to have the bulgogi party on the 9th, but let me know if any day mike is here works for you guys. And we can do it then! Perhaps New Years?
Okay for the bulgogi but mike won't be here.
Oh, nevermind, mike wants to come. So can't do next Sunday.
We can do it in Monday! Mike is leaving on Friday
I will have work on Monday, so it'll have to be around 6ish. Is that okay?
Yeah. My last day is the 7th. Is that bad? Oh goodness, im sorry.
Not unless you want something specifically.
Awesome. So yes, the 29th. Let's say around 630.
Ahh. I thought that's where it was.
Ummm, so was that a no for tonight? Hahah. I realized that we digressed and talked about the bulgogi party instead. Also, what restaurant are you guys going to?
Hello fancy face! I miss you. How's it going?
